{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_31","type":"agent_message","text":"I have enough to start patching. The Liquibase jar already contains `dbchangelog-latest.xsd`, so the remaining issue there is that the current metadata only includes that one file for `5.0.1`; I need to confirm whether `5.0.3` needs a broader resource pattern. Separately, the Spring Boot failure is a straight class-by-name load, so I’m checking which nested condition classes need explicit reflection reachability."}}
